org.gradoop.common.model.impl.id

Class GradoopId

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.common.model.impl.id.GradoopId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<GradoopId>, org.apache.flink.core.io.IOReadableWritable, org.apache.flink.types.CopyableValue<GradoopId>, org.apache.flink.types.Key<GradoopId>, org.apache.flink.types.NormalizableKey<GradoopId>, org.apache.flink.types.Value

    public class GradoopId
extends Object
implements org.apache.flink.types.NormalizableKey<GradoopId>, org.apache.flink.types.CopyableValue<GradoopId>
    Primary key for an EPGM element.

    This implementation reuses much of the code of BSON's ObjectId (org.bson.types.ObjectId) to guarantee uniqueness. Much of the code is copied directly or has only small changes.

    See Also:

    references to: org.bson.types.ObjectId, Serialized Form
